Apply any function to the chain.

Useful for reusing in a chain of operations.

Example:
    ```py
    def parse_stem(chain):
        return chain.map(
            lambda file: file.get_file_stem()
            output={"stem": str}
        )

    chain = (
        DataChain.from_storage("s3://my-bucket")
        .apply(parse_stem)
        .filter(C("stem").glob("*cat*"))
    )
    ```
